# Atlarium

Atlarium is a habitat knowledge platform for aquariums, marine tanks,
coldwater systems, terrariums, paludariums and vivariums.

## Atlarium Habitat Database MCP

Atlarium Habitat Database MCP is a public read-only Model Context Protocol
server for structured habitat data. It gives AI agents access to animal and
plant profiles, habitat products, care requirements, environmental parameters,
species compatibility, guides and habitat planning tools.

Production MCP endpoint:

- https://mcp.atlarium.bio/mcp

Healthcheck:

- https://mcp.atlarium.bio/health

Server card:

- https://mcp.atlarium.bio/.well-known/mcp/server-card.json

Human documentation:

- https://atlarium.bio/mcp

Client setup:

- https://atlarium.bio/mcp/openai-agents
- https://atlarium.bio/mcp/claude
- https://atlarium.bio/mcp/cursor
- https://atlarium.bio/mcp/windsurf
- https://atlarium.bio/mcp/vscode
- https://atlarium.bio/mcp/antigravity
- https://atlarium.bio/mcp/smithery
- https://atlarium.bio/mcp/chatgpt

Repository:

- https://github.com/techgardeners/atlarium-mcp

Important limits:

- Public read-only tools only
- No write tools
- No workspace tools
- No user, auth, admin, journal, schedule or measurement data
- Compatibility and suggestions are advisory and should be verified for each
  real habitat setup
